messages.message: So this one time, I was packing Jeremy's lunch...
Well, he didn't want one this day...

newsArticles.title: So much I want to say,' Trump's ex-lawyer Cohen says as he exits prison early
newsArticles.synopsis: There is so much I want to say and intend to say. But now is not the right time. Soon

newsArticles.title: Clawing back normality: Bangkok cat cafe reopens after virus shutdown
newsArticles.synopsis: As Thailand’s capital cautiously reopens many restaurants shuttered over coronavirus fears, the feline “employees” of the Caturday Cafe are back at work.

newsArticles.title: Five-year-old stopped on U.S. highway wanted to buy Lamborghini, police say
newsArticles.synopsis: A trooper stopping a car with a suspected “impaired driver” on a U.S. highway on Monday was bemused to find a 5-year-old in the driver’s seat, the Utah Highway Patrol tweeted.

newsArticles.title: 'Darth Vader' enforces lockdown in Philippine village
newsArticles.synopsis: Dressed as “Star Wars” characters, local officials in the Philippines are out and about to enforce strict quarantine measures while also handing out relief packages..
